，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"689533c4fdfb8d8edc87017c6d5a3fd5cbe284af","tid":1542050,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"平權失敗邊個最開心？"},{"pid":"d212cc6dd03e718f9c87e73174bb3dc63d86e797","tid":1542050,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689533c4fdfb8d8edc87017c6d5a3fd5cbe284af","tid":1542050,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"平權失敗邊個最開心？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"張曉明，蟈人"},{"pid":"090886f8c91c82ef8a0b4efcd8812345bb1f0d19","tid":1542050,"uid":19037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"鬼鬼鬼你老母咩 想BNO轉BC全部入來<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1496533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg